article_title: The 'Notorious RBG' takes over Saturday Night Live's 'Weekend Update'
article_text:
Supreme Court Justice Ruth Bader Ginsburg gives pretty hilarious and biting interviews in real life — “not 100 percent sober” ringing any bells? — but Kate McKinnon’s version of the “Notorious RBG” on Saturday Night Live’s “Weekend Update” may just take the cake.

From jokes about her morning exercise routine to her sexy dreams about Bruno Mars, it definitely seems like this version of Ginsburg has no reason to be stepping down from the court anytime soon.

Plus, she came up with a great new catchphrase — “You just got Gins-burned!”
